title: Play UK - Issue 239 2014.pdf Gooner
description:
Play has been the voice of PlayStation gaming since 1995, and it has a well-earned reputation for forthright reviews, of getting best and biggest game exclusives and a commitment to high-quality videogames journalism that has seen Play outclass and outlast all of its rivals. Its focus is on PlayStation 3 gaming, bringing its readers all the best PS3 coverage out there, but also offers both an irreverent and intelligent look at all things PlayStation for the discerning PlayStation gamer. Please note: Digital versions of the magazines do not include the covermount items or supplements that you would find on printed editions.
